===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|accion|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|action|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|actio|āctiō|act of doing or making|lang=la}}, from {{term|actus|āctus|lang=la}}, perfect passive participle of {{term|ago|agō|do, act|lang=la}}, + action suffix {{term|-io|-iō|lang=la}}; see [[act]].

